bug.author: oveddan
bug.summary: PoseNet camera demo - MobileNet with quant bytes of 1 shows no poses
bug.description:
To reproduce: Open the <denchmark-link:https://storage.googleapis.com/tfjs-models/demos/posenet/camera.html>current version of the posenet demo</denchmark-link>
Select 1 from the quantBytes drop down. No poses show up in the output. quantBytes of 2 and 4 work fine. cc <denchmark-link:https://github.com/tylerzhu-github>@tylerzhu-github</denchmark-link>
